\[\frac{1}{f}=\frac{1}{a'}-\frac{1}{a_0-l} = \frac{(a_0-l)a'}{a_0-l-a'} = \frac{6.5 \cdot 13.5}{6.5 - 13.5} = -12.54\;\;\text{см}\]
